Ranger Help for: make satchel
==============================

SYNTAX:      make satchel
USAGE:       Wilderness
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     30
SKILL TYPE:  survival

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to expand their wildcraft forage pouch.
The Ranger needs 3 hide scraps, 2 sinew, and 2 binding fiber. Hide
scraps and sinew come from skinning corpses, while binding fiber comes
from forage.

If your pouch is full before you have the right materials, use
'forage stores' to see what is taking space and
'forage discard <component> [amount]' to throw away spare supplies.

Each successful upgrade increases wildcraft capacity, up to the
maximum a Ranger can maintain in the field.
